Package: shinycroneditor
Title: Shiny Cron Expression Input Widget
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Harmen",
                  family = "van der Veer",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "harmen@datalab.nl")
Description: A widget for Shiny apps to handle schedule expression input, using the 'cron-expression-input' JavaScript component. Note that this does not edit the 'crontab' file, it is just an input element for the schedules.
Imports: htmltools, htmlwidgets
Suggests: shiny
